 presencia formal clave en obras que abarcan desde grandes nombres como Joyce, Huxley, Mann o Proust, hasta autores de novela policiaca o de la narrativa hispánica de los últimos años.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023z9783111318264oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2023z9783110998719oZDB-207-IBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869424540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968694245423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968694245/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-207-IBVb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DSPb2023